gw.plugin.lookup

Class LookupMetaColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.plugin.lookup.LookupMetaColumn
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LookupColumn

    public class LookupMetaColumn
extends java.lang.Object
    Each LookupMetadata template consists of one or more LookupMetaColumn instances, these LookupMetaColumn's are used to describe the expected input types for a lookup. The end-user must use this as to validate expected input values types against actual input types.
